{"tid":1043170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"流浪地球主角吳京愛國比人踢爆 笑撚到肚痛","createTime":"2019-03-02T05:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T12:34:41.000Z","uid":108814,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7ded73feba4f19516ca9ec55f5cf0c5f9b5171","tid":1043170,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:23:36.000Z","msg":"《戰狼》吳京被爆逃稅過億人民幣粉絲失望︰原來係假愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳京是一個香港籍演員，而老婆謝楠是美國籍，兒子是英國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛國又逃税又外國籍<br />\n想點呀 同中國膠官一樣<br />\n又外國籍又貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係5毛最愛國 錢又少又交足税<br />\n呢班粉腸中國有咩事<br />\n第一個走去外國避難"},{"pid":"d408408d5c846018494198de0784431b01cb4e2f","tid":1043170,"uid":56462,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"發覺中國人錢其實好易賺<br />\n<br />\n成班中國人戇鳩鳩<br />\n只要打住民族主義旗號就賺到錢<br />\n<br />\n21世紀仲係咁<br />\n<br />\n都幾可悲幾可笑"},{"pid":"085e93b0d37d8d5d83b320e0e16e278015b31212","tid":1043170,"uid":25367,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"有外國籍係為咗方便跨境執行任務"},{"pid":"dfbc07db0d5a1fbfcd27466ef2ed0d8512e78cdf","tid":1043170,"uid":9315,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"佢個愛國3歲細路都睇得出係假啦<br />\n冇愛國旗號又揚曬中國旗又打柒外國人既話戰狼套垃圾點會有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本就係利用愛國賺錢"},{"pid":"aab46e240e977c19676a9faba7551f5641a2ded6","tid":1043170,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d408408d5c846018494198de0784431b01cb4e2f","tid":1043170,"uid":56462,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"發覺中國人錢其實好易賺<br />\n<br />\n成班中國人戇鳩鳩<br />\n只要打住民族主義旗號就賺到錢<br />\n<br />\n21世紀仲係咁<br />\n<br />\n都幾可悲幾可笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:29:51.000Z",